Entropic as in from entropy, the damage channel</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="135"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_1</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Entropic attacks have a {singleSTR} strength chance ({repeatingSTR} for repeating attacks) chance to apply [abilityred]Atrophy[/abilityred] for {duration}, a stacking debuff that reduces damage output by {damageReduction}</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ataki entropiczne mają szansę o sile {singleSTR} ({repeatingSTR} dla ataków wielokrotnych) na spowodowanie [abilityred]atrofii[/abilityred] na {duration}, sumującego się osłabienia, które zmniejsza zadawane obrażenia o {damageReduction}.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Mod description
Atrophy is a status effect relating to the Entropy damage channel</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sedating Decay Component</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Uspokajający rozkład</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Mod name</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="120"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Entropic attacks have a {singleSTR} strength chance ({repeatingSTR} for repeating attacks) chance to apply [abilityred]Slow Movement[/abilityred] and reduce accuracy by {accuracyDebuff} for {turns}.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ataki entropiczne mają szansę o sile {singleSTR} ({repeatingSTR} dla ataków wielokrotnych) na spowodowanie [abilityred]spowolnienia[/abilityred] i zmniejszenia celności o {accuracyDebuff} na {turns}.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Mod description</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="120"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EFFECT_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sedated</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Uspokojenie</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Title of status effect</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="120"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EFFECT_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit has [abilityred]Slow Movement[/abilityred] and {accuracyDebuff} reduced accuracy.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka cierpi na [abilityred]spowolnienie[/abilityred] i ma celność zmniejszoną o {accuracyDebuff}.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Status effect description</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="120"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sedate</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Środek uspokajający</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Modifier name</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="120"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_3</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{strengthChance} strength chance to apply [abilityred]Slow Movement[/abilityred] and {accuracyDebuff} reduced accuracy for {turns}.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Szansa o sile {strengthChance} na spowodowanie [abilityred]spowolnienia[/abilityred] i zmniejszenia celności o {accuracyDebuff} na {turns}.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Modifier effect description</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_4</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Entropic Radiation Emitter</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Radiator entropiczny</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Mod name</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="150"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_4</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Enemy units adjacent to this unit get {damage} damage and have a {strength} strength chance to get [abilityred]Atrophy[/abilityred] for {turns}[turn/] at the end of each [turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wrogie jednostki sąsiadujące z tą jednostką otrzymują {damage} pkt. obrażeń i mają szansę o sile {strength} na [abilityred]atrofię[/abilityred] na {turns}[turn/] po zakończeniu każdej [turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Mod description</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_5</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Entropy Retaliation Component</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Odwet entropiczny</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Mod name</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="120"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENTROPY_MOD_5</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Whenever this unit is damaged by an enemy unit within a {hexrange} hex range, that unit gets {atrophystacks} stack of [abilityred]Entropic Decay[/abilityred] for {turns} and {entropydamage} damage.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gdy ta jednostka odnosi obrażenia od wrogiej jednostki w promieniu {hexrange} pól, napastnik otrzymuje {atrophystacks} poz. [abilityred]rozkładu entropicznego[/abilityred] na {turns} i {entropydamage} pkt. obrażeń.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Mod description
